<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Confirmation de votre achat</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333333;
        }
        p {
            color: #666666;
        }
        .order-summary {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .activation-key {
            background-color: #e8f8ff;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #007acc;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #999999;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <h1>Thank you for your purchase, {{ mail }} !</h1>
    <p>We thank you for your order. Here is a quick summary:</p>

    <div class="order-summary">
        <p><strong>Order made :</strong> {{ date_order|date("d/m/Y") }}</p>
        <p><strong>Chosen api :</strong> {{ product_name }}</p>
        <p><strong>Selected offer :</strong> {{ offer_name }}</p>
        <p><strong>Total :</strong> {{ product_price }}â‚¬</p>
    </div>

    <p>Your api activation key is :</p>
    <div class="activation-key">
        {{ activation_key }}
    </div>

    <p>If you have any questions or problems, please do not hesitate to contact us.</p>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>2024 - Marketplace. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
